Title: Smith's Textbook of Endourology (2 Volume Set)
Author: আর্থার ডি. স্মিথ এমডি
Summary:
Smith's Textbook of Endourology (2 Volume Set)
Albert Einstein College of Medicine, Bronx, NY. Major two-volume clinical reference for urologists and residents. Discusses general principles and specific endourologic procedures, using both open and minimally invasive approaches. Abundant halftone illustration. 154 contributors, 121 U.S.
